        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <p style="max-width: 475px;">Both outer fabric and inner lining of the suit are supplied by Italian mills based just outside of Milano. Our main fabric is a mid-weight satin weave that combines comfort, durability, color depth and drape like nothing you've seen before. The satin weave features a more subtle optical structure than the more common twill and the discrete percentage of stretch adds comfort and durability without compromising the touch. Added to that, we've lightly brushed the surface, lending a warmer hand feel and a deep and cloudy matt shade. We've matched it with tonal Italian herringbone pocket lining and interior seam binding for a subtle structural contrast on the inside. In plain words, materials and sartorial details that epitomize our beloved phrase 'free of compromise, full of love'.</p>
