            <h4 class="impactTitles" style="color: #999999;"><strong>Fabric</strong>:  Cotton Farmed in USA, carded and spun in Taranto, Italy. Elastane - researching origin. Elastane spun in Kahramanmaraş, Turkey. Cotton-elastane yarn twisted in Taranto, Italy. Fabric woven in Taranto or woven and finished in Milan, Italy. <strong>Lining</strong>:  Cotton - researching origin. Yarn spun in Asia - researching origin. Weaving in Pakistan. Dye and finish in Coarezza, Italy. <strong>Fusing</strong>:  Cotton origin - researching origin. Produced in Germany. <strong>Buttons</strong>:  Real horn from water buffalo, India (Chennai Bombay and Delhi) Button produced in Bergamo, Italy. <strong>Hook & Bar</strong>:  Raw material - researching origin. Manufactured in Italy. <strong>Zipper</strong>:  Raw material origin Kurobe, Japan. Manufacturing made in Alenquer, Portugal. <strong>Puller</strong>:  Raw material origin Kurobe, Japan. Manufacturing made in Ascoli Piceno, Italy. <strong>Sewing Thread</strong>:  Researching origin. <strong>Hangtag</strong>:  Paper pulp and hangtag produced in Dongguan, China. Polyester produced, spun and twisted to string in Dongguan, China. <strong>Care Label</strong>:  Polyester, spun, woven and printed in Dongguan, China. <strong>Main Label</strong>:  Polyester, spun and woven in Dongguan, China. <strong>Garment construction</strong>:  Cut and sewn in Esposende, Portugal. Trimmed and packed in Vila Nova de Famalicao, Portugal. Washed in Varzea, Portugal. <strong>Packaging</strong>:  Plastic from the UK, bag made in Vojens, Denmark. <strong>Storage & shipping</strong>:  Stored in and shipped from Tallinn, Estonia Shipped in carton boxes made in Värnamo, Sweden.</h4>
